http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/telangana/10-peacocks-die-after-drinking-poison-laced-water/article14009429.ece

Ten peacocks died after drinking poison-laced water at Kushal Nagar near Siddipet on Monday. The issue came to light late in the night.According to District Forest Officer, Sridhar Rao, the birds fell unconscious after drinking the water and died later. The post-mortem reports revealed that they died after consuming poison.It was suspected that the birds either consumed pesticide-mixed water or tablets that are used to kill these birds. Remains of the birds were buried by the Forest Department officials.